<p>Didn't like it much. It's basically just a generic &quot;it catches you and kills you&quot; monster without anything particularly scary or otherwise interesting about it, and I can't shake off the feeling that parts of the article are only here to ad shock value (how it slowly pulls victims appart, Members of Epsilon-9 being &quot;at first&quot; reluctant to use flamethrowers on their teammates. What relelvance does that anecdote even have in an acquisition report?).</p>
